               <interp inst="t17671209-79" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17671209"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17671209-79" type="date" value="17671209"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17671209-79-off420-c535" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-defend700 t17671209-79-off420 t17671209-79-verdict423"></join>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17671209-79-off420-c536" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-defend702 t17671209-79-off420 t17671209-79-verdict423"></join>
         
               <p>96, 97. (L.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17671209-79-defend700" type="defendantName">
                     James 
                     Peal 
                  <interp inst="t17671209-79-defend700" type="surname" value="Peal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-defend700" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-defend700" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
                
             and 
               
                  <persName id="t17671209-79-defend702" type="defendantName">
                     James 
                     Furver 
                  <interp inst="t17671209-79-defend702" type="surname" value="Furver"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-defend702" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-defend702" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
                
             were indicted for <rs id="t17671209-79-off420" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-off420" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-off420" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a handkerchief, value 18 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17671209-79-victim704" type="victimName">
                     Nathan 
                     Weatherall 
                  <interp inst="t17671209-79-victim704" type="surname" value="Weatherall"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-victim704" type="given" value="Nathan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-victim704" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-off420 t17671209-79-victim704"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17671209-79-cd421" type="crimeDate">Dec. 6</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-off420 t17671209-79-cd421"></join>. ++</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17671209-79-person705">
                  Nathan 
                  Weatherall 
               <interp inst="t17671209-79-person705" type="surname" value="Weatherall"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person705" type="given" value="Nathan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person705" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On last Sunday se'nnight at night, about a quarter after six, going into <placeName id="t17671209-79-crimeloc422">St. Dunstan's church</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17671209-79-crimeloc422" type="placeName" value="St. Dunstan's church"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17671209-79-crimeloc422" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-off420 t17671209-79-crimeloc422"></join>, Mr. Paine asked, me if I had not lost my handkerchief; I felt, and said I had; he directly laid hold of the two prisoners by each hand one; I saw him take my handkerchief from Furver.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17671209-79-person706">
                  William 
                  Paine 
               <interp inst="t17671209-79-person706" type="surname" value="Paine"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person706" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person706" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw Peal take out the prosecutor's handkerchief from his pocket, and deliver it to Furver, who put it in his right-hand pocket; I told the gentleman of it, and took hold of the prisoners, and took the handkerchief out of Furver's pocket, and delivered it.</p>
               <p>Peal's defence.</p>
               <p>I had been to dine with a relation, and when I came to the church they laid hold of me.</p>
               <p>He called 
               <persName id="t17671209-79-person707">
                  Charles 
                  Richmond 
               <interp inst="t17671209-79-person707" type="surname" value="Richmond"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person707" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person707" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             and 
               <persName id="t17671209-79-person708">
                  Mary 
                  Clark 
               <interp inst="t17671209-79-person708" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person708" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-person708" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>Furver's defence.</p>
               <p>I saw the handkerchief lying, and I took it up.</p>
               <p>Both <rs id="t17671209-79-verdict423" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-verdict423" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17671209-79-punish424" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-punish424" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-79-punish424" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="branding"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-defend700 t17671209-79-punish424"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-79-defend702 t17671209-79-punish424"></join>
               B
            </rs>.</p>
            </div1>
